  <shortDescription><![CDATA[<p>This very special and brand new itinerary is packed with exciting experiences that you’ll never forget! You’ll be based in your hotel in Harstad for the duration of your stay - a small, attractive harbour town just south of Trømso and north-east of the Lofoton Islands - and venture out each day into the surrounding wintery landscape of this amazingly scenic and untouched part of the world. </p>]]></shortDescription>
